msgstr "Patrullas policiales"

msgctxt "2084"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "56_Man With a Past"
msgid "Hey, don't start doing anything shady, okay? Cops are everywhere, and I can't have them thinkin' I've got anything to do with you!"
msgstr "Oye, no hagas nada sospechoso cerca de mí. ¡Vas a llamar la atención de los policías!"

msgctxt "68_Man With a Past"
msgid "The police in Kamurocho are on high alert. They have sent many of their officers out on patrol around the town to make sure they catch anyone acting suspicious."
msgstr "La policía de Kamurocho está en alerta máxima. Mandaron a muchos de sus agentes a patrullar para asegurarse de atrapar a cualquiera que actúe de forma sospechosa."

msgctxt "80_Man With a Past"
msgid "There are two types of officers: some stand guard in place and watch their surroundings, while others follow a patrol and approach shady individuals to question them."
msgstr "Hay dos tipos de policías: unos que hacen guardia en un lugar y vigilan el entorno, y otros que recorren una ruta acercándose a personas sospechosas para interrogarlas."

msgctxt "92_Man With a Past"
msgid "Running down the street will attract the attention of patrolling officers.\\r\n"
"You may want to enter first-person mode with <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> and check for officers before moving quickly."
msgstr "Correr por la calle atraerá la atención de los agentes patrullando.\\r\n"
"Quizás quieras entrar en modo primera persona con <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> y revisar si hay policías antes de pasar corriendo por un lugar."

msgctxt "104_Man With a Past"
msgid "This information has been added as a <Color:14>memo<Color:Default>.\\r\n"
"Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu.\\r\n"
"You can access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button."
msgstr "Esta información ha sido añadida como una <Color:14>nota<Color:Default>.\\r\n"
"Lee las <Color:14>notas<Color:Default> seleccionando <Color:14>Notas<Color:Default> en el menú de pausa.\\r\n"
"Puedes acceder al menú de pausa con el botón <Action:Button_Options@Adventure>."

msgctxt "116_Man With a Past"
msgid "Be careful out there."
msgstr "Ten cuidado, amigo."

